Popular online skit maker, Debo Adebayo aka Mr Macaroni has announced engagement to his longtime colleague, Kemi Ikuseedun who plays the role of “Mummy Wa” in his skits. The couple took to their social media pages to share the news with fans. Mr Macaroni, via his verified Instagram page, posted a series of pictures with the caption “Engagement Today, Wedding Tomorrow.”   A revolution in African farming     Nod to repeat      Tinubu, govs, minister, others attend Aisha Buhari’s…   Kemi took to her verified Instagram page @Kemz_mama, and posted a short wedding clip with the watermark “Kemi Ikuseedun + Debo Adebayo” She wrote: “DaddyWa finally paid mummy wa’s bride price @mrmacaroni + @kemz_mama.” Fans and friends have taken to the comment section of their posts to celebrate with them.